==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: grass-of-Parnassus
<hw>grass-of-Parnassus</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Any of various usually
evergreen bog plants of the genus <gen>Parnassia</gen> having broad
smooth basal leaves and a single pale buttercuplike flower.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> parnassia, grass of Parnassus.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

